Test Drive Le Mans (PAL)
------------------------
Ripped: Nothing.
Downsampled: Nothing.
Source: GD dump.

This game is very small, so I've added a huge dummy file and optimized file order. Loadings are
very fast now. Echelon's release of this game had VMU icon glitched (icon files were not present),
but they're working fine on this release.

Note that although this is the PAL version, it works fine on NTSC-U consoles (60hz) with A/V or
VGA Box.

Enjoy this wonderful racing game with the best quality possible.

Features of my release:
- Not corrupted files at all, it was made with GD dump files.
- Dummied for 700mb CDs. It means faster loading times.
- Used custom file order based on GD's. It helps loading times and Dreamcast reader noise.
- Selfboot.

About the game:
- It has VGA Box support.

Other comments:
- "Extras" folder in the pack contains some useless stuff.